## Notes on writing this inventory

- **Capture verbatim quotes** from the candidate. *"I felt invincible"* / *"Every job looks pretty chill after that"* — direct quotes are gold for later cover letters.
- **Capture specific names** — people, deals, companies. They unlock reference candidates and warm-intro paths later.
- **Capture specific numbers** — revenue, team size, raise amounts, deal sizes.
- **Mark audience-calibrated framings** — when the same fact can be framed for different audiences, capture both versions.
- **Don't sanitize.** This file is private. Capture the honest version, including parts that won't appear externally.
